{"word":"Serpent","slug":"serpent","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Serpent</b> Satan appears in the form of, to Eve<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=15'>Gen 3:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=47&chapter=11&verse=3'>2Co 11:3</a><br/> Subtlety of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=1'>Gen 3:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=21&chapter=10&verse=8'>Ecc 10:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=10&verse=16'>Mat 10:16</a><br/> Curse upon<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=15'>Gen 3:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=49&verse=17'>Gen 49:17</a><br/> Feeds upon the dust<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=3&verse=14'>Gen 3:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=65&verse=25'>Isa 65:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=7&verse=17'>Mic 7:17</a><br/> Unfit for food<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=7&verse=10'>Mat 7:10</a><br/> Venom of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=24'>Deu 32:24</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=33'>Deu 32:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=20&verse=16'>Job 20:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=58&verse=4'>Psa 58:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=140&verse=3'>Psa 140:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=23&verse=32'>Pro 23:32</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=28&verse=6'>Act 28:6</a><br/> The staff of Moses transformed into<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=4&verse=3'>Exo 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=7&verse=15'>Exo 7:15</a><br/> Fier